- Naku!

27
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,539
Hindi ko 'yan tinutukoy.

28
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,120
Alam ko, Boss.

29
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,520
Ikaw naman si Boss Sila, kung tutuusin.

30
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:33,160
Ikaw ay matatag, matiyaga,
at kasingtatag ng bato.

31
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,960
Boss, nag-aalala ka pa rin ba
tungkol sa deal kagabi?

32
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:52,360
Mukhang medyo stressed ka.

33
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:55,160
Nakasimangot ka na
simula nang umalis tayo.

34
